An apple tree seed grows into an Apple tree which produces cooking apples. Players with a Farming level of 27 can grow Apple trees in a fruit tree patch. This gives 22 experience. An additional 8.5 experience is granted for harvesting, and 1199.5 exp can be gained by checking the health of the trees. An Apple tree will take 16 hours to grow completely.

You can pay a farmer 9 raw sweetcorn (may be noted) to take care of it.

Found in bird nests.
